## FRONTEND STATUS — PARTIALLY DONE

Some frontend pages/components already exist. When writing PLAN.md, mark these as
`[PARTIAL]` and describe only what remains to be built for each. Do NOT regenerate
code for already-completed parts unless explicitly asked.

### Known partially-done areas (update this list as you discover more):
- Auth pages (Register, Login) — UI scaffolded, API wiring incomplete
- Dashboard shell — tab layout exists, data fetching not connected
- Tutor profile form — fields rendered, no submit/validation logic
- Session messaging UI — component exists, no WebSocket or polling connected

For any page marked `[PARTIAL]`, the task in PLAN.md should read:
`[ ] Wire [PageName] to backend: [specific endpoints to connect]`
NOT `[ ] Build [PageName] from scratch`.

